---
title: Seared Cod with Mediterranean Bean & Tomato Salad
description: This light dish is great for a warm spring night. Delicate cod is seared until flaky and served over a refreshing salad of cannellini beans, green beans, and tomatoes. If you have the time, feel free to marinate the salad for up to 12 hours!
